In reference to the source code modifications and the parameters modifications, all the info is in Table 2 (allometric parameters) and former section 2.5 (LAI parameters).
 
Just a synthesis:
 
 - To run D-CLM4.5 for evergreen forests: The parameter file used is D-CLM4.5_EvergreenSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric parameters). No source code modifications
 
- To run D-CLM4.5 for deciduous forests: The parameter file used is D-CLM4.5_DeciduousSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric and LAI parameters). No source code modifications
 
- To run D-Litton for evergreen forests: Changes needed in both source code (file CNAllocationMod.F90) and parameter file (changes in allometric parameters). 
The parameter file used is D-Litton_EvergreenSite_parameters.nc
The source code modifications are in the file CNAllocationMod.F90

- To run D-Litton for deciduous forests: Changes needed in both source code (file CNAllocationMod.F90) and parameter file (changes in allometric and LAI parameters).
The parameter file used is D-Litton_DeciduousSite_parameters.nc
The source code modifications are in the file CNAllocationMod.F90
 
- To run F-Evergreen for evergreen forests: The parameter file used is F-Evergreen_EvergreenSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric parameters). No changes in code
 
- To run F-Evergreen for deciduous forests: The parameter file used is F-Evergreen_DeciduousSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric and LAI parameters). No changes in code
 
- To run F-Deciduous for evergreen forests: The parameter file used is F-Deciduous_EvergreenSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric parameters). No changes in code

- To run F-Deciduous for deciduous forests: The parameter file used is F-Deciduous_DeciduousSite_parameters.nc (changes in allometric and LAI parameters). No changes in code



